	   <tr><td colspan=2>What I did to level rather quickly during these levels were kill the sirens in OOT.&nbsp;&nbsp;The ones I'm talking about are on the twin rock islands, there's one on the left island, and two on the right island.  You can also kill the goblins at the lower levels, maybe 13-15.<br>I grouped here with a friend at 12-13, becuase I was having problems soloing them, if Lull messed up and I got both sirens, they could kill me, but at 14 I was able to take them on without a problem.<br>Their respawn time is OK, at the lower levels you can be fighting nonstop, you might have to take breaks to heal.  As you get to 16-17, you will kill them so fast that you have a lot of downtime waiting for the next one to spawn... I just found something to do in RL for the couple minutes between each spawn, I got a book to read a page or two of at each downtime.<br>I was a bit twinked at that point, so I don't know what level an untwinked bard would have to be to solo them, but it's definitely worth a try.  It's OK money and no bad faction, and pretty good experience.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
